{
  "font_size": 0.4,
  "font_color": "#FFFFFF",
  "background_alpha": 0.5,
  "background_color": "#9C27B0",
  "Stroke": "none",
  "type": "AIsubtitle",
  "lang": "zh",
  "version": "eng-1.2.0-Index-johns-pen-lite",
  "body": [
    {
      "content": "假设你构建了一个工作流程",
      "from": 0.06,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 1.9
    },
    {
      "content": "但它还没有达到你期望的效果",
      "from": 1.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 4.64
    },
    {
      "content": "这种情况我经常遇到",
      "from": 4.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 6.32
    },
    {
      "content": "顺便说一句",
      "from": 6.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 6.74
    },
    {
      "content": "我通常会快速搭建一个简易系统",
      "from": 6.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 8.82
    },
    {
      "content": "但它表现不如我预期",
      "from": 8.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 11.65
    },
    {
      "content": "问题在于你要将精力集中在哪些环节才能改进",
      "from": 11.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 16.009
    },
    {
      "content": "事实证明，基因工作流程包含许多不同组件",
      "from": 16.009,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 18.909
    },
    {
      "content": "优化某些组件可能比其他组件更有效",
      "from": 18.909,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 24.63
    },
    {
      "content": "你选择专注方向的能力对改进速度影响巨大",
      "from": 24.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 29.97
    },
    {
      "content": "能让你在系统中实现改进的速度",
      "from": 29.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 32.29
    },
    {
      "content": "我发现其中一个最大预测因素",
      "from": 32.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 35.5
    },
    {
      "content": "团队效率和质量如何",
      "from": 35.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 38.35
    },
    {
      "content": "是否能有效执行纪律性错误分析流程",
      "from": 38.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 43.01
    },
    {
      "content": "以确定改进方向",
      "from": 43.01,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 45.62
    },
    {
      "content": "这是一个重要技能",
      "from": 45.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 47.36
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们看看如何在研究代理示例中执行错误分析",
      "from": 47.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 52.549
    },
    {
      "content": "我们在前一视频中进行了错误分析",
      "from": 52.549,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 56.089
    },
    {
      "content": "发现经常遗漏关键点",
      "from": 56.089,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 59.65
    },
    {
      "content": "就像人类专家撰写特定主题文章时",
      "from": 59.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 63.65
    },
    {
      "content": "现在你已发现有时会遗漏关键点的问题",
      "from": 63.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 68.29
    },
    {
      "content": "该如何着手解决",
      "from": 68.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 70.76
    },
    {
      "content": "在工作流程的众多步骤中",
      "from": 70.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 73.83
    },
    {
      "content": "几乎任何步骤都可能导致遗漏关键点的问题",
      "from": 73.83,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 78.89
    },
    {
      "content": "例如",
      "from": 78.89,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 79.67
    },
    {
      "content": "可能第一个语言模型生成的搜索词不够优质",
      "from": 79.67,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 83.51
    },
    {
      "content": "导致搜索内容不准确",
      "from": 83.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 85.98
    },
    {
      "content": "未能找到正确文章",
      "from": 85.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 87.98
    },
    {
      "content": "或者使用的网络搜索引擎效果不佳",
      "from": 87.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 91.42
    },
    {
      "content": "市面上存在多种网络搜索引擎",
      "from": 91.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 93.2
    },
    {
      "content": "实际上我常用多个搜索引擎处理个人应用",
      "from": 93.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 97.52
    },
    {
      "content": "有些效果更好",
      "from": 97.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 99.4
    },
    {
      "content": "或者网络搜索本身并无问题",
      "from": 99.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 101.76
    },
    {
      "content": "但将搜索结果列表交给语言模型时",
      "from": 101.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 104.64
    },
    {
      "content": "可能处理不当",
      "from": 104.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 106.2
    },
    {
      "content": "未能选出最佳文档下载",
      "from": 106.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 108.8
    },
    {
      "content": "可能网络抓取环节问题较少",
      "from": 108.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 111.2
    },
    {
      "content": "在这种情况下",
      "from": 111.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 111.96
    },
    {
      "content": "假设你能准确获取网页内容",
      "from": 111.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 114.16
    },
    {
      "content": "但将网页内容输入语言模型后",
      "from": 114.16,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 116.46
    },
    {
      "content": "模型可能忽略部分已抓取文档中的要点",
      "from": 116.46,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 121.71
    },
    {
      "content": "事实证明有些团队会凭直觉选择组件改进",
      "from": 121.71,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 124.99
    },
    {
      "content": "有时这种方法奏效",
      "from": 124.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 129.03
    },
    {
      "content": "但有时会导致数月工作却进展甚微",
      "from": 129.03,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 130.37
    },
    {
      "content": "因此不应依赖直觉选择组件改进",
      "from": 130.37,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 137.15
    },
    {
      "content": "与其凭感觉决定改进哪个组件",
      "from": 137.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 142.17
    },
    {
      "content": "我认为进行系统性错误分析更好",
      "from": 142.17,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 145.99
    },
    {
      "content": "以更深入理解工作流程各环节",
      "from": 145.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 149.189
    },
    {
      "content": "特别是我会经常检查执行轨迹",
      "from": 149.189,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 151.86
    },
    {
      "content": "即每个步骤后的中间输出",
      "from": 151.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 154.84
    },
    {
      "content": "为了了解哪些组件的性能不佳",
      "from": 154.84,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 159.74
    },
    {
      "content": "意思",
      "from": 159.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 160.2
    },
    {
      "content": "说",
      "from": 160.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 160.7
    },
    {
      "content": "远不如人类专家的表现",
      "from": 160.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 163.67
    },
    {
      "content": "因为这可能表明存在显著改进的空间",
      "from": 163.67,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 168.04
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们看一个例子",
      "from": 168.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 169.08
    },
    {
      "content": "如果我们让研究代理撰写一篇关于黑洞信号最新新闻的论文",
      "from": 169.08,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 174.47
    },
    {
      "content": "也许输出结果",
      "from": 174.47,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 175.97
    },
    {
      "content": "像这样的搜索关键词",
      "from": 175.97,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 176.99
    },
    {
      "content": "搜索黑洞理论",
      "from": 176.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 178.07
    },
    {
      "content": "爱因斯坦事件视界",
      "from": 178.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 179.43
    },
    {
      "content": "望远镜",
      "from": 179.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 179.87
    },
    {
      "content": "无线电等",
      "from": 179.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 181.25
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我会让专家查看这些内容并判断",
      "from": 181.25,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 184.23
    },
    {
      "content": "这些是否是撰写黑洞信号最新发现论文的合理网络搜索关键词",
      "from": 184.23,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 190.35
    },
    {
      "content": "在这种情况下专家可能认为这些搜索结果看起来没问题",
      "from": 190.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 194.82
    },
    {
      "content": "它们与我作为人类的做法非常相似",
      "from": 194.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 197.72
    },
    {
      "content": "然后我查看网页搜索结果并检查返回的网址",
      "from": 197.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 203.7
    },
    {
      "content": "网页搜索会返回许多不同网页",
      "from": 203.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 206.99
    },
    {
      "content": "也许其中一个网页显示",
      "from": 206.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 209.28
    },
    {
      "content": "一名小学生声称破解了天体物理学领域三十年的黑洞之谜",
      "from": 209.28,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 214.64
    },
    {
      "content": "儿童新闻",
      "from": 214.64,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 215.35
    },
    {
      "content": "这看起来不像经过严格同行评审的文章",
      "from": 215.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 219.23
    },
    {
      "content": "或许检查所有网页搜索返回的文章",
      "from": 219.23,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 223.82
    },
    {
      "content": "会让你得出返回过多博客或通俗新闻文章的结论",
      "from": 223.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 229.91
    },
    {
      "content": "而不足以撰写高质量的研究报告",
      "from": 229.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 235.62
    },
    {
      "content": "最好也检查其他步骤的输出结果",
      "from": 235.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 238.92
    },
    {
      "content": "也许代理筛选出最佳五篇资料",
      "from": 238.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 241.21
    },
    {
      "content": "最终可能得到",
      "from": 241.21,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 242.23
    },
    {
      "content": "天体儿童新闻",
      "from": 242.23,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 243.07
    },
    {
      "content": "太空球",
      "from": 243.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 243.57
    },
    {
      "content": "二千空间趣味新闻",
      "from": 243.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 245.11
    },
    {
      "content": "等等",
      "from": 245.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 245.91
    },
    {
      "content": "正是通过查看这些中间输出",
      "from": 245.91,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 249.57
    },
    {
      "content": "才能初步判断每个步骤输出的质量",
      "from": 249.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 253.75
    },
    {
      "content": "引入一些术语",
      "from": 253.75,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 255.05
    },
    {
      "content": "所有中间步骤的输出集合",
      "from": 255.05,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 259.19
    },
    {
      "content": "通常被称为该代理运行的轨迹",
      "from": 259.19,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 262.709
    },
    {
      "content": "其他资料中也会见到的术语",
      "from": 262.709,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 266.529
    },
    {
      "content": "单个步骤的输出有时称为片段",
      "from": 266.529,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 270.45
    },
    {
      "content": "来自计算机可观测性领域的术语",
      "from": 270.45,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 274.63
    },
    {
      "content": "用于分析计算机行为",
      "from": 274.63,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 277.51
    },
    {
      "content": "在这门课中我多次使用了'轨迹'一词",
      "from": 277.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 280.68
    },
    {
      "content": "我会较少使用'片段'这个词",
      "from": 280.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 282.8
    },
    {
      "content": "但你可能在互联网上看到这两个术语",
      "from": 282.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 285.4
    },
    {
      "content": "通过阅读轨迹",
      "from": 285.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 287.1
    },
    {
      "content": "可以初步判断哪些组件可能存在最大问题",
      "from": 287.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 292.44
    },
    {
      "content": "为了更系统地进行分析",
      "from": 292.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 294.6
    },
    {
      "content": "关注系统表现不佳的案例会很有帮助",
      "from": 294.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 300.62
    },
    {
      "content": "也许有些论文完全符合要求",
      "from": 300.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 304.28
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我可以把这些放在一边，尝试构建一组示例，其中",
      "from": 304.28,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 307.88
    },
    {
      "content": "无论什么原因，你的研究代理的最终输出并不令人满意",
      "from": 307.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 312.62
    },
    {
      "content": "然后专注于这些示例",
      "from": 312.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 314.88
    },
    {
      "content": "这就是我们称之为错误分析的原因之一",
      "from": 314.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 317.26
    },
